title: Texas primaries a weathervane for Democrats
text:
Texas primaries a weathervane for Democrats 11:14am GMT - 02:01 
Primary contests for the 2018 mid-term elections are underway in Texas, where Democrats are hoping for a groundswell of enthusiasm, but also watching to see whether progressives could push the party in a direction that might alienate more moderate voters.
